1. *Poziv* je stigao na vrijeme. (The invitation arrived on time.)
2. On je dobio *poziv* da prisustvuje događaju. (He was invited to attend the event.)
3. Oni su poslali *poziv* svim prijateljima. (They sent out invitations to all their friends.)
4. On je primio *poziv* da postane član komisije. (He was invited to become a member of the commission.)
5. Ona je odbila *poziv* da prisustvuje konferenciji. (She declined the invitation to attend the conference.)
6. Svi smo dobili *poziv* da sudjelujemo na zabavi. (We all received an invitation to attend the party.)